TextEng: I think we need to change your tactics.
Text: 네 전술을 바꿔야 할 것 같아.

TextEng: I think I'll do better off on my own.
We need to change the distance you stay away from me.
Stay close.
Medium distance.
Far distance.
Nevermind.
Could we change how quickly you decide to heal me?
Text: 날 치유하는 시점을 바꿀 수 있을까?

TextEng: Heal me if I become somewhat injured (below 75% of total hit points).
Text: 좀 다치면 치유해 줘 (전체 생명력의 75% 미만).

TextEng: Heal me if I become wounded (below 50% of total hit points).
Text: 부상을 입으면 치유해 줘 (전체 생명력의 50% 미만).

TextEng: Heal me if I become seriously wounded (below 25% of total hit points).
Text: 심각하게 다치면 치유해 줘 (전체 생명력의 25% 미만).

TextEng: Could you not search all the time?
Could you please search when we move around?
Could you use more stealth when we travel?
Could you stop being so stealthy all the time?
If I fail to open a locked door or chest please come to my aid.
Text: 잠긴 문이나 상자를 여는 데 실패하면 도와줘.

Text: 잠긴 문이나 상자를 여는 데 실패하면 날 돕지 마.

TextEng: I don't want to change anything else right now.
Text: 지금은 다른 걸 바꾸고 싶지 않아.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> That seems a little expensive. I'll give you 100.
We need change way you do stuff.
Text: 우리 네가 하는 방식 바꿔야 해.

TextEng: Me no want you here no more.
Text: 나 이제 너 여기 원하지 않아.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> That seem high. Me give 100 only.
Here's your 150 gold. Welcome aboard, Sharwyn.
Here be you 150 gold. Now you be me slave, Sharwyn.
Text: 여기 너의 금화 150개. 이제 너 나의 노예야, 샤윈.

TextEng: I'll be going now.
Me go now.
125? Deal.
Here's your 200 gold. Welcome aboard, Sharwyn.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> That seems a little expensive. I'll give you 150.
Here be 200 gold. Now you be me slave, Sharwyn.
Text: 여기 금화 200개. 이제 너 나의 노예야, 샤윈.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> That seem high. Me give 150 only.
Here's your 250 gold. Welcome aboard, Sharwyn.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> That seems a little expensive. I'll give you 200.
Here be 250 gold. Now you be me slave, Sharwyn.
Text: 여기 금화 250개. 이제 너 나의 노예야, 샤윈.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> That seem high. Me give 200 only.
175? Deal.
225? Deal.
You change how far away you stay.
Text: 네가 얼마나 멀리 떨어져 있는지 바꿔.

TextEng: You need change how you heal me.
Text: 네가 날 치유하는 방법 바꿔야 해.

TextEng: You not search all time no more.
Text: 너 더 이상 항상 탐색하지 마.

TextEng: You search all time when we move.
Text: 우리 움직일 때 너 항상 탐색해.

TextEng: You stop sneaking so quiet now.
Text: 너 이제 그렇게 조용히 잠행하는 거 그만해.

TextEng: You start sneak quiet now.
If me fail on locked door or chest you help me.
Text: 내가 잠긴 문이나 상자 실패하면 너 나 도와.

TextEng: If me fail on locked door or chest you not help me.
Text: 내가 잠긴 문이나 상자 실패하면 너 나 돕지 마.

TextEng: Me not want change anything else now.
Text: 나 지금 다른 거 바꾸고 싶지 않아.

TextEng: You heal if me sort of hurt (below 75% of total hit points).
Text: 내가 좀 다치면 너 치유해 (전체 생명력의 75% 미만).

TextEng: You heal if me wounded (below 50% of total hit points).
Text: 내가 부상당하면 너 치유해 (전체 생명력의 50% 미만).

TextEng: You heal if me hurt real bad (below 25% of total hit points).
Text: 내가 정말 심하게 다치면 너 치유해 (전체 생명력의 25% 미만).

TextEng: Yes. Go.
No. Stay.
I don't have that kind of gold to spend on a henchman.
Me not got that much gold for spend on you.
Text: 나 너한테 쓸 그렇게 많은 금화 없어.

TextEng: Who are you?
I don't feel like talking right now. Goodbye.
What do you know about the Blacklake district?
I'm looking for someone to help me in my mission.
I work for Lady Aribeth. I have been instructed to find several missing creatures that might be used to find a plague cure.
Text: 아리베스 경을 위해 일하고 있어. 역병 치료제를 찾는 데 사용될 수 있는 여러 실종된 생명체를 찾으라는 지시를 받았어.

TextEng: I work for Lady Aribeth. My mission is confidential.
Text: 아리베스 경을 위해 일하고 있어. 내 임무는 기밀이야.

TextEng: Anything else you can tell me about Blacklake?
Text: 검은호수에 대해 다른 걸 말해줄 수 있어?

TextEng: Actually, I'm looking for some help to assist me on my mission.
Text: 사실, 임무를 도와줄 사람을 찾고 있어.

TextEng: No thanks. Goodbye.
I want to ask you some questions.
Well, I wasn't acting alone.
Yes, that would be me.
Who you be?
Me not wanna talk. Goodbye.
What you knows about Blacklake place?
Text: 너 검은호수 장소에 대해 뭐 알아?

TextEng: Me looks for someone to help on mission.
You hear 'bout other stuff happening in Blacklake?
Text: 너 검은호수에서 일어나는 다른 일 들었어?

TextEng: Me looking for help in me mission.
Text: 나 나의 임무 도와줄 사람 찾고 있어.

TextEng: Me go now.
Me work for lady Aribeth. Me looking for creatures. They are important. They cure plague.
Text: 나 아리베스 부인 위해 일해. 나 생명체들 찾고 있어. 중요해. 역병 치료해.

TextEng: Me working for lady Aribeth. Can't tell you me mission. It secret.
Text: 나 아리베스 부인 위해 일해. 나의 임무 말 못 해. 비밀이야.

TextEng: Me want to ask questions.
Me have lots of help!
Me greatest one there is! Me save city!
So you're working for Aribeth?
Goodbye.
You work for Aribeth?
If you're so interested in fame, why are you standing around here?
Text: 명성에 그렇게 관심이 있다면, 왜 여기 서 있어?

TextEng: If you want fame, why you stand around here?
Text: 너 명성 원하면, 왜 너 여기 서 있어?

TextEng: I wouldn't mind an extra hand. You're in.
Sorry, but I'm not interested. Goodbye.
Me need another man. You in.
Text: 나 다른 사람 필요해. 너 들어와.

TextEng: Sorry, me not interested.
Have you heard any rumors about the cult since you've come here?
Text: 여기 온 이후로 사교에 대한 소문 들었어?

TextEng: You hear any stuff about cult? Me looking for clues.
Text: 너 사교에 대해 뭐 들었어? 나 단서 찾고 있어.

TextEng: Monsters?
So are you going to look into it some more?
So why are you standing around here? Shouldn't you be out scouring the north for this cult?
Text: 그럼 왜 여기 서 있어? 이 사교를 찾아 북쪽을 뒤져야 하는 거 아니야?

TextEng: You gonna try to find out more stuff about the cult and Luskan?
Text: 너 사교랑 러스칸에 대해 더 많은 것 알아낼 거야?

TextEng: Why you stand around here? You supposed to be looking for cult.
Text: 왜 너 여기 서 있어? 너 사교 찾아야 하는 거 아니야.

TextEng: I'd like you to level up. You'd be more useful to me with a little training.
Text: 레벨업했으면 좋겠어. 약간의 훈련으로 더 유용해질 거야.

TextEng: Me want you to level up. You be better with training.
Text: 나 네가 레벨업하길 원해. 훈련하면 나아질 거야.

TextEng: I just want to talk for a while.
Me just wanna talk.
I'd like to know more about you.
I want you to continue your story from before.
Nevermind.
Me wanna know you better. Me think that important.
Text: 나 너 더 잘 알고 싶어. 나 그게 중요하다고 생각해.

TextEng: Me want you continue you story from before.
Text: 나 네가 전에 하던 이야기 계속하길 원해.

TextEng: I cannot idly stand by while people suffer and die.
Text: 사람들이 고통받고 죽어가는 걸 가만히 보고만 있을 순 없어.

TextEng: In times of darkness great heroes must do great deeds. It is how legends are forged.
Text: 어둠의 시대에 위대한 영웅들은 위대한 업적을 이뤄야 해. 그게 전설이 만들어지는 방식이야.

TextEng: Aribeth has promised me gold and riches if I can help her in this.
Text: 아리베스가 이 일을 도우면 금화와 부를 약속했어.

TextEng: Absolutely, Sharwyn. Stick with me and you'll be famous.
Text: 물론이지, 샤윈. 나랑 있으면 유명해질 거야.

TextEng: Forget about that. We have more important matters to attend to.
Text: 그건 잊어. 더 중요한 일이 있어.

TextEng: You not worry, Sharwyn. You stick with me, you be famous!
Text: 걱정 마, 샤윈. 너 나랑 있으면, 너 유명해질 거야!

TextEng: You not think 'bout that no more. We has lots to do.
Text: 너 더 이상 그거 생각하지 마. 우리 할 일 많아.

TextEng: If we're to be companions I'd like to know a little more about you.
Text: 우리가 동료가 될 거라면 너에 대해 좀 더 알고 싶어.

TextEng: I'd like you to continue your story from before, Sharwyn.
Text: 전에 하던 이야기를 계속해줬으면 해, 샤윈.

TextEng: If we be travel together, me want know more 'bout you.
Text: 우리 함께 여행하면, 나 너에 대해 더 알고 싶어.

TextEng: Me want you keep talking 'bout story you start before.
Text: 나 네가 전에 시작한 이야기 계속 말하길 원해.

TextEng: How about telling me a tale, Sharwyn? You are a bard, after all.
Text: 이야기 하나 들려줄래, 샤윈? 어쨌든 넌 음유시인이잖아.

TextEng: I'd like you to continue your story from before.
You tells me good story, Sharwyn? You is bard, after all.
Text: 너 나한테 좋은 이야기 해줘, 샤윈? 너 음유시인이야, 어쨌든.

TextEng: Me want you to continue you story from before.
Text: 나 너 전에 하던 이야기 계속하길 원해.

TextEng: You again? What, are you following me around?
Text: 또 너야? 뭐, 날 따라다니는 거야?

TextEng: I'm surprised to see you here, Sharwyn.
So you were conscripted into service by Aribeth?
How much would it cost to hire your services?
Text: 네 서비스를 고용하는 데 얼마나 들어?

TextEng: Goodbye.
I could use someone by my side.
Do you have any information on the cult behind the Wailing Death?
Text: 울부짖는 죽음 뒤의 사교에 대한 정보 있어?

TextEng: I don't need anything right now.
I did my duty.
I know, I'm great. What can I say?
Me do duty.
Me am so great! Me am so great!
Text: 나 정말 대단해! 나 정말 대단해!

TextEng: So you're working for Aarin Gend?
Text: 그럼 아린 겐드를 위해 일하고 있어?

TextEng: You work for Aarin Gend? Me work for Aarin too!
Text: 너 아린 겐드 위해 일해? 나도 아린 위해 일해!

TextEng: Goodbye.
Have you heard any rumors as to where the Words could be?
Text: 언령이 어디 있을지에 대한 소문 들었어?

TextEng: Why are you standing around here? Shouldn't you be looking for these Words?
Text: 왜 여기 서 있어? 이 언령들을 찾아야 하는 거 아니야?

TextEng: You heard any rumors about where Words be? Me want to find them.
Text: 너 언령이 어디 있는지에 대한 소문 들었어? 나 그것들 찾고 싶어.

TextEng: Why you stand here? You should look for Words.
Text: 왜 너 여기 서 있어? 너 언령 찾아야 해.

TextEng: I could use some help in my search for the Words.
Sorry, I'm not interested.
Me could use you in me search for Power Words.
Text: 나 권능의 언령 찾는 데 너 필요해.

TextEng: Me not like you.
It is good to see you again, Sharwyn.
I'm getting sick of seeing you every time I turn around!
Text: 돌아설 때마다 너를 보는 게 지겨워지고 있어!

TextEng: Do you know anything about the Words of Power, Sharwyn?
Text: 권능의 언령에 대해 뭔가 알아, 샤윈?

TextEng: I would be honored to have you join up with me again, Sharwyn.
I don't need any help right now.
Yes.
No, not now.
Yes.
No.
And just what skills do you have?
And if I don't seek adventure and excitement?
Text: 그리고 내가 모험과 흥분을 추구하지 않는다면?

TextEng: What skills you has?
And if me not seeks adventure and excitement?
Text: 그리고 나 모험이랑 흥분 추구하지 않으면?

TextEng: You left behind a life of riches?
You leaves behind riches?
You're a local girl, are you?
You local girl, huh?
Me see lots people die. Me not like it. Me want help them.
Text: 나 많은 사람들 죽는 거 봤어. 나 좋아하지 않아. 나 그들 돕고 싶어.

TextEng: Neverwinter need hero to save it. If me save Neverwinter then me be hero.
Text: 네버윈터 구할 영웅 필요해. 나 네버윈터 구하면 나 영웅이야.

TextEng: Me get lots gold if me help Neverwinter!
Text: 나 네버윈터 도우면 금화 많이 받아!

TextEng: Oblivion? What are you talking about?
Oblivion? What you talks about?
No need to be so melodramatic about it.
You not needs be so whiney about it.
Text: 너 그거에 대해 그렇게 징징댈 필요 없어.

TextEng: Do you have any advice you can give me about my mission?
Text: 내 임무에 대해 줄 수 있는 조언이 있어?

TextEng: You got any tip you give me 'bout this mission?
Text: 너 이 임무에 대해 나한테 줄 조언 있어?

TextEng: Tell me about the Blacklake district.
Tell me 'bout Blacklake district.
Anything else?
I think that's enough talking for now.
Me not want talk no more.
Text: 나 더 이상 얘기하고 싶지 않아.

TextEng: Me not think me see you here, Sharwyn.
Text: 나 여기서 너 볼 거라고 생각 안 했어, 샤윈.

TextEng: You again? Is you following me like some stupid puppy?
Text: 또 너야? 너 바보 강아지처럼 나 따라다니는 거야?

TextEng: Aribeth force you to come serve here?
How much it cost for you work for me again?
Text: 다시 나 위해 일하는 데 얼마나 들어?

TextEng: You know stuff 'bout that cult that spread plague?
Text: 너 역병 퍼뜨린 사교에 대해 뭐 알아?

TextEng: Me need someone like you for help me.
Text: 나 나 도와줄 너 같은 사람 필요해.

TextEng: Me not need nothing right now.
Monsters?
Where?
Me glad for see you again, Sharwyn.
Me sick of you! Everywhere me go you be there!
Text: 나 너 지겨워! 내가 어디 가든 너 거기 있어!

TextEng: You know stuff 'bout Words of Power, Sharwyn?
Text: 너 권능의 언령에 대해 뭐 알아, 샤윈?

TextEng: Me be happy if you join me 'gain, Sharwyn.
Text: 너 다시 나랑 함께하면 나 행복해, 샤윈.

TextEng: Me not need no help right now.
Where?
And if I said I was looking for work?
Text: 그리고 내가 일자리를 찾고 있다고 말한다면?

TextEng: And if me say me looks for work?
I might be looking for a henchman.
Maybe me looks for henchman.
My name is <FirstName>. Pleased to meet you.
Who are you that you interrogate possible employers?
I never said I would hire *you*, did I?
Me called <FirstName>. Is nice to meet you.
Who you that you questions me like that?
Me not say me hires *you*.
Why not tell me who you are, first?
You tells me who you is, first.
My business is my own.
What me doing no concern you.
You seem pretty sure of yourself.
You sure of youself, huh?
You're right... you do seem arrogant.
You is right. You arrogant.
I think such confidence is admirable.
Me thinks is good you so sure.
Text: 나 생각해 너 그렇게 확신하는 거 좋아.

TextEng: It is my duty to assist. There is nothing more to be said.
Text: 돕는 것이 내 의무야. 더 말할 것 없어.

TextEng: Me has duty to help. Need not say more.
Text: 나 도울 의무 있어. 더 말할 필요 없어.

TextEng: Why do you want to know? I asked first.
Text: 왜 알고 싶어? 내가 먼저 물었잖아.

TextEng: Why you wants to know? Me ask first.
Text: 왜 너 알고 싶어? 나 먼저 물었어.

TextEng: Who knows what might happen, Sharwyn?
Text: 무슨 일이 일어날지 누가 알아, 샤윈?

TextEng: Nobody know what happen, Sharwyn.
Text: 아무도 무슨 일 일어날지 몰라, 샤윈.

TextEng: I doubt it, if that's all you seek.
Me doubts it, if that all you seeks.
Text: 나 의심스러워, 그게 너 추구하는 전부면.

TextEng: I agree.
Me agrees.
Tell me now.
Sure, another time.
I don't want to hear your stories, I'm sure.
Text: 네 이야기 듣고 싶지 않아, 확실해.

TextEng: You tells me now.
Okays, some other time.
Me not want to hear you stories, me sure.
Text: 나 너의 이야기 듣고 싶지 않아, 나 확실해.

TextEng: Yes, it does actually.
Yeah, it do!
Why would she do that?
You don't sound as if you approve.
She had sense, obviously.
Why she do that?
You no sound like you approves.
She have sense, me thinking.
What about you? Were you saddened by his death?
She sounds like a terrible woman.
So she returned to her magic?
What about you? You not be sad when he die?
Text: 너는 어때? 너 그가 죽었을 때 슬프지 않았어?

TextEng: She sound like bad woman.
So she goes back to magic?
Did you?
You must have felt foolish.
I take it your mother wasn't happy about that?
Text: 네 어머니는 그것에 대해 행복하지 않았겠네?

TextEng: Who was this man, then?
You must feels like fool, huh?
I guess you mother not happy?
Text: 나 생각엔 너의 어머니 행복하지 않았어?

TextEng: Who this guy, then?
That was selfish of you.
Love can do that.
So what happened?
That be selfish of you.
Love do that, me thinking.
So what happen?
This couldn't have gone on long.
Why didn't you simply make a decision?
People act like idiots when they're in love.
The not goes on for long, me thinking.
Text: 그거 오래 안 갔을 거야, 나 생각해.

TextEng: Why you not makes decision?
Peoples be dumb when they is in love.
So did she have Dannen killed?
So you killed her?
An unpleasant scene, I would bet.
So she gets Dannen killed, huh?
So you kills mother?
Not good scene, me thinking.
You chose Dannen?
You chose Lord Farthingdon?
You chooses bard?
You chooses Lord whatshisname?
What did you do then?
How could you do that to your mother?
You did the only thing you could.
Text: 할 수 있는 유일한 일을 했어.

TextEng: What you do then?
How you does that to mother?
You does only thing you could.
Text: 너 할 수 있는 유일한 일 했어.

TextEng: She still lives?
Mother be alive?
Why would you even want her healed?
Is there nothing that can be done?
Text: 할 수 있는 게 아무것도 없어?

TextEng: Perhaps I could help her.
Text: 아마 내가 그녀를 도울 수 있을 거야.

TextEng: Why you even wants her healed?
Nothing be done?
Maybe me could helps.
Is this the potion you're talking about?
Perhaps we shall find it on our travels.
Text: 아마 여행 중에 찾을 수 있을 거야.

TextEng: Just don't let your search interfere with my mission.

TextEng: This was bad news?
This be bad news?
No, tell me the rest now.
I'll hold you to that promise.
Why would I want to hear about your sad breakup with Dannen?
Text: 왜 다넨과의 슬픈 이별에 대해 듣고 싶겠어?

TextEng: No, you tells me more now.
Me holds you to that promise.
Text: 나 너 그 약속 지키게 할 거야.

TextEng: What went wrong, then?

TextEng: What go wrong?

TextEng: Uh-oh, that does sound bad...
Did you ask why they invited you?

Uh-oh... that sound bad.

Oldest story in the book.

Is oldest story in book.

TextEng: Me woulds never treat you so bad, Sharwyn.

Text: 너 다넨이 아직도 그녀랑 함께 있다고 확신해?

TextEng: Perhaps you should just let it be, then.
Dannen should be free from the spell, at least, no?

TextEng: Lady Onaris hurt you. She deserves to be revealed for what she is.

TextEng: Love? Oh, ick.

Sounds promising.
Love? Bah!
This better be good.
It sound promising.
"Three Who Are One?"

I only asked a question.

Okays, we go.
Me only ask question.
That is a beautiful story...

TextEng: Do you believe that about love?

TextEng: It just big story, me thinks.

TextEng: What are you going to do with it?

Monsters?

In fight you use melee weapon, not range weapon.

TextEng: Only that me brings your loud mouth along.

TextEng: I'm doing this because it's right, not to be a hero.

TextEng: Bah. It's a foolish business.

TextEng: I don't think I'm a legend...

TextEng: You gets ahead of things, no?

TextEng: Ha! You is on own after this.
Who know what happens?
Me too, Sharwyn.
Aren't you being a bit premature?
Ha! You're on your own after this.
Who knows what will happen?
